{"code":0,"message":"","data":null,"sentence":{"phonemes":[],"text":"I am, after all, a reasonable man. Since your girl is saddened by her cat becoming a mushroom, it means our intentions differ. Different paths lead to different destinations. I respect everyone's opinion, but I do not believe what I did was wrong.","words":[]}}
